Chiang Mai, Thailand1,578 contributions
Iconic Lady Buddha Statue!
This enormous statue overlooks the sea towards the city of Da Nang. It is the tallest statue in the area and is situated within a wonderful park village. There was no admittance charge! Also many great views of Da Nang from this point!
