The intricate carvings and statues of the Lady Buddha are truly breathtaking
I found the experience to be very enlightening and calming. The place itself is a beautiful sight to behold. The intricate carvings and statues of the Lady Buddha are truly breathtaking and make for a great photo opportunity. The grounds are well maintained and the atmosphere is peaceful and serene.
