Very impressive to visit
Dec 2019
We used a grab taxi from the hotel we stayed at on the beach. It is short ride and is much more impressive when you get there than it appears from a distance. There is more than just the Lady Buddha, such as Temples and also unexpectedly quite tame monkeys although I would not suggest trying to pet them at all. We spent a little over an hour there.
