Karolina S
Sheffield, UK13 contributions
Great statue and even better views!
Mar 2020
We rented a scooter for a day and decided to go up the 'Monkey Mountain'. The views on the way up are spectacular. We stopped a few times just to appreciate it fully. The Lady Buddha statue is massive and quite impressive. The surrounding gardens are lovely too and of course the pagodas. And we also saw monkey which is a massive BONUS for me :) overall a great half a day out.
